These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-1::.
Music-Genre: punk, folk, ambient, blues
Pet: turtle, hedgehog, horse, goldfish
1. Pet:hedgehog is on the left of Pet:turtle##1
2. Music-Genre:punk == Pet:goldfish##1
3. Pet:horse is on the right of Pet:turtle##1
4. Music-Genre:folk is on the left of Pet:goldfish##1
5. Music-Genre:blues is on the left of Pet:turtle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |   3    |    4    |
| Music-Genre          | blues | ambient | folk | punk   |
| Pet   | hedgehog  | turtle     | horse   | goldfish |

