.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-2::.
Transport: tram, jet-ski, snowmobile, boat
Music-Genre: d&b, soul, funk, ambient
1. Transport:boat == Music-Genre:soul##1
2. Transport:tram is on the far right##1
3. Transport:jet-ski is on the right of Transport:boat##1
4. Transport:boat is on the right of Music-Genre:funk##1
5. Music-Genre:soul is on the left of Music-Genre:d&b##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |      2      |    3    |     4      |
| Transport   | snowmobile | boat | jet-ski | tram    |
| Music-Genre   | funk    | soul      | d&b | ambient |

